1. *Vodiš* poštu po selima. (You deliver mail to villages.)
2. Često *vodiš* ljude do tačne lokacije. (You often lead people to the exact location.)
3. Učenici *vode* svoje učitelje na ekskurziju. (The students are taking their teachers on a trip.)
4. Ona *vodi* svoju porodicu u šoping. (She is taking her family shopping.)
5. Trebalo bi da *vodiš* računa o zdravlju. (You should take care of your health.)
6. Često *vodiš* razgovore s prijateljima. (You often have conversations with friends.)
7. *Vodiš* brigu o svom domu. (You take care of your home.)